This is the international space station location program written in C++ by Brad Bettencourt (See license). This was built using C++ 11 and requires libcurl4 & or libcurl-dev to be installed before running the make file. 

To run/install. 

1.) make
2.) ./iss

To exit the application at any time please use ctrl^C. 

Usage:

Display's the current lat and long of the iss. Updates every 2 seconds. Takes no flags.

version 1.0
